import React from 'react'

import { InboxOutlined, UploadOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons'
import {
  Button,
  Checkbox,
  Col,
  Form,
  InputNumber,
  Radio,
  Rate,
  Row,
  Select,
  Slider,
  Switch,
  Upload,
  Input,
} from 'antd'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const { Option } = Select

const formItemLayout = {
  labelCol: { span: 6 },
  wrapperCol: { span: 14 },
}

const Profile = () => (
  <Wrapper>
    <Form
      name='validate_other'
      {...formItemLayout}
      initialValues={{
        'input-number': 3,
        'checkbox-group': ['A', 'B'],
        rate: 3.5,
      }}
      style={{ maxWidth: 600 }}
    >
      <Form.Item
        label='Description'
        name='Description'
        rules={[{ required: true, message: 'Please enter your description!' }]}
      >
        <Input />
      </Form.Item>
      <Form.Item
        name='Paid-By'
        label='Paid By'
        hasFeedback
        rules={[{ required: true, message: 'Please select who paid!' }]}
      >
        <Select placeholder='Please select who paid'>
          <Option value='china'>China</Option>
          <Option value='usa'>U.S.A</Option>
        </Select>
      </Form.Item>

      <Form.Item
        name='select-multiple'
        label='Paid For'
        rules={[
          {
            required: true,
            message: 'Please select the people involved!',
            type: 'array',
          },
        ]}
      >
        <Select mode='multiple' placeholder='Please select the people involved'>
          <Option value='red'>Red</Option>
          <Option value='green'>Green</Option>
          <Option value='blue'>Blue</Option>
        </Select>
      </Form.Item>

      <Form.Item label='InputNumber'>
        <Form.Item name='Amount' noStyle>
          <InputNumber min={1} max={100000} />
        </Form.Item>
      </Form.Item>
    </Form>
  </Wrapper>
)

const Wrapper = styled.div`
  background: white;
  padding: 5rem;
  max-width: 50rem;
`

export default Profile
